Description: # zi-i18n
        A Experimental Internationalization
        
        example:
        
        ```python
        #in "example.py" file
        from zi_i18n import I18n
        
        i18n = I18n("locale", "en_US")
        print(i18n.translate("example.text"))
        
        #in "locale/en_US.zi.lang" file
        <!example.text: "Test">
        #output: Test
        ```
        
